author: Garry M
title: Garry M
text:
Have been using Ink Station for sometime.
Prices are very good and have never had a faulty or wrong cartridge delivered.
The best part is how rapid the order is processed and delivered, this being the case with every order.
Its a credit to the team at IS
Regards,
Garry (Small Business Owner in Wodonga)
